title: 0-Day Week of 2014.04.09
description:
Soooo, yet another week of comics. Gets tedious right?



Please post some poop jokes to lighten the mood


Two turds were out for a walk.

One of them got run over.

Then then the other one said "C'mon diarrhea, let's go" 


I told that one to one of my sister's kids during a Christmas dinner and he actually fell off his chair laughing. My sister did not like the joke though.
